+# SwapOnBase notes
+
+I picked Aerodrome on Base and wired `swapUsdcForWeth` to its real router at
+`0xcF77a3Ba9A5CA399B7c97c74d54e5b1Beb874E43`.
+
+Aerodrome is the deepest native DEX on Base by TVL/liquidity, so the contract
+routes the USDC -> WETH swap through its volatile pool using the Aerodrome pool
+factory `0x420DD381b31aEf6683db6B902084cB0FFECe40Da`.
